Package: vtschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Vermont School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Vermont Agency of
    Education (AOE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from the
    Vermont Education Dashboard and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Data includes enrollment by grade level for all public schools and districts
    in Vermont from 2017 to present.
